---
title: Teriyaki Tofu with Roasted Bok Choy and Basmati Rice
description: Looking for a tasty midweek dinner option? Try cooking up our Teriyaki Tofu with Bok Choi & Rice in just 20 minutes for a balanced and tasty dinnertime.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/teriyaki-tofu-6619289b-eb8ee134.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/teriyaki-tofu-5d7a74b36f627e75b945fcc6-39258edf.pdf
